column1: Physician-Related Services/ Professional and Emergent Oral Healthcare Services

The Agency pays enhanced rates for qualified trauma care services. The enhancement of 275% is applied to the lesser of the Agency’s maximum allowable fee or the provider’s billed amount. The enhancement is subject to funds availability.
Please refer to Section E in the Medicaid Provider Guide (Physician Services) for specific criteria related to trauma care services.
